schools.name: Vista Academy Of Visual And Performing Arts

data.description: Looking for a beautiful starter home with lots of upgrades at a reasonable price? Here it is ... nice upgraded kitchen, appliances, countertops, range, hood, 2 bedrooms, spacious living room has a spilt system AC and more.  This is a desirable corner lot home, allows parking for 4 plus cars on a new concrete driveway or perfect for a large RV!.  Home also has brand new concrete patio perfect for the next family get together or holiday, for barbecuing.  The updated iron gated fence surrounds the also new faux ivy hedge leaf & vine, providing privacy. Close to Downtown Vista with restaurants, stores and 20 minutes further is Downtown Oceanside and beaches.
